channel.title: The system cannont find the path specified
channel.description: I run my client, and its pops up along with the batch file box. Yet my client runs and works fine, i get a message in the dos box saying The system cannont find the path specified. Any ideas how to stop this?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: July 21, 2009, 05:47:13 am[/size][hr]Nvm just fixed this as soon as i posted this, because my clients packaged it was loading the files from elsewhere.
